oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Flower Tracing (Taylor Swift) 01
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Swift, Taylor, 1989-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Pen and ink tracing for a poster for Taylor Swift's sold out show at the Gillette Stadium in Foxborough, MA as part of her Fearless Tour in 2010. The drawing would be transferred to a linoleum or woodblock carving and then used to apply ink to the poster paper.
